{
  "stem": "9987.4",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The man asked, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said [SPEAKING POLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That-- that means, I don't understand German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The biggest mistake the Jewish people that pretended to be Christian made, when they-- when they talked German.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The minute they talked German, the German knew, because Poles hardly knew any German.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He ask again in-- in-- in-- in German, what did you come here for?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't understand German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I'm showing him the documents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the Ukrainian policeman is translating to me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He is asking you what did you come here for?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I said, I got an order from the arbeitzamp to come to-- to present myself to go to work to Germany.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Looked straight in his eyes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Didn't give a blink.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he looks at me, and I look at him, and he finally hands me back over the documents.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he says, [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That means--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--go.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now, if I didn't die at that time, I'll live a million years.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I came back to town, and I was looking what's going to happen to find out, like they say, a spy.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I found out that since the German did not keep the promise to the Ukrainians and never had intentions to give them independence, that was western Ukraine, the Ukrainians probably were going to make a revolution.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had a conference over there of all high command German officers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But the Germans found out what was going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the whole city was on alert, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and nothing happened.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I went back to my place over there, to-- gave them the news, gave them the information, and that thing was going on until the 29th of April, 1944.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The only time I was hungry was in prison.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
